examples.en: The blood sprayed onto the wall.
Water sprayed all over the floor.
The soda sprayed from the bottle.
They sprayed the crops with a pesticide.
He sprayed the garden to get rid of pests.
He sprayed the paint evenly over the surface.
They are sprayed with oil to prevent corrosion.
We were sprayed by water from the crashing waves.
This medication for athlete's foot is atomized so that it can be sprayed on from an aerosol can.
